WEBVTT

00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:03.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>BRIGHTLY</b></Default>

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:07.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm telling you, puberty
syndrome actually does exist!</b></Default>

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just look. This proves it.</b></Default>

00:00:09.750 --> 00:00:11.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a proper look, please.</b></Default>

00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:13.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After looking at the messages
in her friend group</b></Default>

00:00:13.630 --> 00:00:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my little sister's body
developed bruises.</b></Default>

00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's such a ridiculous thing.
Can't happen in real life.</b></Default>

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't an occult manga</b></Default>

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why won't you just believe me?
You aren't even trying to!</b></Default>

00:00:25.329 --> 00:00:28.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what you say</b></Default>

00:00:32.289 --> 00:00:34.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa's lost it.</b></Default>

00:00:34.539 --> 00:00:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think he's gone insane.</b></Default>

00:00:38.670 --> 00:00:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:00:40.420 --> 00:00:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do something to clear up
this tension in the air.</b></Default>

00:00:46.789 --> 00:00:49.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}ALUMNI ASSOCIATION INFORMATION</b></Default>

00:00:53.670 --> 00:00:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:01.540 --> 00:02:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:24.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 1ST</b></Default>

00:02:24.580 --> 00:02:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The matchmaking party
last night was so fun.</b></Default>

00:02:27.210 --> 00:02:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}We never did end up getting down
to the truth about you guys.</b></Default>

00:02:29.879 --> 00:02:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}DISSONANT NOTES</b></Default>

00:02:31.460 --> 00:02:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't you get along
with Kamisato, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:02:34.289 --> 00:02:36.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, we get along better
now than before.</b></Default>

00:02:36.669 --> 00:02:38.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-That's better?
-Yeah. It is.</b></Default>

00:02:39.289 --> 00:02:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Then I guess it's okay.
-What is?</b></Default>

00:02:41.830 --> 00:02:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you're about to find out.</b></Default>

00:02:43.789 --> 00:02:45.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much, Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:02:45.919 --> 00:02:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're very welcome.</b></Default>

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Later, dude.</b></Default>

00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you dare tell Yuma
anything you don't need to.</b></Default>

00:02:55.419 --> 00:02:56.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, it's too late for that.</b></Default>

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:57.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:02:57.919 --> 00:03:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already complained
to his voicemail last night.</b></Default>

00:03:00.750 --> 00:03:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told him that
not only were you late</b></Default>

00:03:02.669 --> 00:03:04.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you said you were lovey-dovey
with a handsome firefighter</b></Default>

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in your introduction</b></Default>

00:03:05.919 --> 00:03:07.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and destroyed
my first matchmaking party.</b></Default>

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had no choice but to tag along
with Chiharu and company</b></Default>

00:03:10.789 --> 00:03:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to balance out the numbers.</b></Default>

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:13.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can tell that to Kunimi.</b></Default>

00:03:13.960 --> 00:03:16.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I will.
I'm seeing him today.</b></Default>

00:03:16.419 --> 00:03:18.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that all you wanted to say?</b></Default>

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:19.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh. For me.</b></Default>

00:03:19.629 --> 00:03:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, for you?</b></Default>

00:03:21.129 --> 00:03:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry. I'm done.
You can go ahead.</b></Default>

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, Saki.</b></Default>

00:03:27.629 --> 00:03:31.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, I heard you and Saki
went to the same high school.</b></Default>

00:03:31.250 --> 00:03:33.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Now I know
you're friends with Kamisato.</b></Default>

00:03:33.669 --> 00:03:34.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:03:34.750 --> 00:03:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was the first person
I spoke to on campus.</b></Default>

00:03:37.830 --> 00:03:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She even helps me out
on occasion</b></Default>

00:03:39.539 --> 00:03:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the volunteer organization
I put together.</b></Default>

00:03:42.169 --> 00:03:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For schooling assistance?</b></Default>

00:03:43.789 --> 00:03:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, you knew about it?</b></Default>

00:03:46.539 --> 00:03:49.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never really saw Kamisato
as one to volunteer.</b></Default>

00:03:49.460 --> 00:03:52.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, really? I actually think
it's typical of Saki.</b></Default>

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, she's aspiring
to be a nurse</b></Default>

00:03:55.039 --> 00:03:57.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so she can support
her firefighter boyfriend</b></Default>

00:03:57.129 --> 00:03:58.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as best she can.</b></Default>

00:03:58.250 --> 00:04:01.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, sorry. Please don't
tell Saki I told you that.</b></Default>

00:04:01.629 --> 00:04:04.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I probably wouldn't have
the chance to, so don't worry.</b></Default>

00:04:05.539 --> 00:04:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, Akagi, why'd you decide
to major in nursing?</b></Default>

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:11.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because as a nurse</b></Default>

00:04:11.379 --> 00:04:14.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can be there for the people
who require the most help.</b></Default>

00:04:15.039 --> 00:04:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:04:16.250 --> 00:04:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So is that why you believe
in the #DREAMING posts</b></Default>

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and act as a hero of justice?</b></Default>

00:04:21.379 --> 00:04:23.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You even cosplayed as a nurse.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:04:24.629 --> 00:04:27.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like I cosplay
every time I help people.</b></Default>

00:04:27.790 --> 00:04:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday</b></Default>

00:04:29.829 --> 00:04:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the middle school kids
from the volunteer class</b></Default>

00:04:32.170 --> 00:04:34.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I wanted to dress up
for them.</b></Default>

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you always go out of your way
to save others?</b></Default>

00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shouldn't I?</b></Default>

00:04:38.629 --> 00:04:40.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest, I never thought
someone like you</b></Default>

00:04:40.709 --> 00:04:43.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would believe in occult rumors
like puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:04:44.790 --> 00:04:47.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what do you need
from me, Akagi?</b></Default>

00:04:47.579 --> 00:04:50.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't expect you to want
to attend something like this</b></Default>

00:04:50.629 --> 00:04:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but people
from our middle school</b></Default>

00:04:52.379 --> 00:04:54.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are planning a reunion
at the end of the month</b></Default>

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so, yeah.</b></Default>

00:04:55.629 --> 00:04:56.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ALUMNI ASSOCIATION INFORMATION</b></Default>

00:04:56.750 --> 00:04:58.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right. I wouldn't go.</b></Default>

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:01.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure it'd be fun for those
that have things to brag about.</b></Default>

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:02.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, that is true.</b></Default>

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:05.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I could gloat about
how I'm dating Mai now.</b></Default>

00:05:05.709 --> 00:05:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if you did go
to the reunion, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nobody could say anything.</b></Default>

00:05:09.879 --> 00:05:11.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but I'm not dating her</b></Default>

00:05:11.290 --> 00:05:13.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to flaunt my celebrity
girlfriend around others.</b></Default>

00:05:13.670 --> 00:05:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really? Then why
are you dating her?</b></Default>

00:05:17.209 --> 00:05:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that we can be
happy together.</b></Default>

00:05:20.250 --> 00:05:22.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please stop it.</b></Default>

00:05:22.250 --> 00:05:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's so embarrassing.</b></Default>

00:05:24.079 --> 00:05:25.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gotta go. Bye.</b></Default>

00:05:25.670 --> 00:05:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Help others out
in moderation, okay?</b></Default>

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's that?</b></Default>

00:05:30.629 --> 00:05:32.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because when you try
to change the future</b></Default>

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:35.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>something even worse
might end up happening instead.</b></Default>

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, okay. Got it.</b></Default>

00:05:42.079 --> 00:05:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think you got it at all.</b></Default>

00:05:51.420 --> 00:05:53.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SHONAN PERSONAL INSTRUCTION
CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:05:56.879 --> 00:05:58.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is going
in the opposite direction</b></Default>

00:05:58.709 --> 00:06:00.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so people often think
it's going to be negative.</b></Default>

00:06:00.959 --> 00:06:03.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's about the size
of the energy, so it always...</b></Default>

00:06:03.829 --> 00:06:06.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must be the underclassman
Kunimi told me about.</b></Default>

00:06:06.459 --> 00:06:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you solve it by calculating
the momentum first.</b></Default>

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You listening?
-Yes, ma'am.</b></Default>

00:06:13.540 --> 00:06:14.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You get it?</b></Default>

00:06:14.629 --> 00:06:16.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-No, I don't.
-[sighs]</b></Default>

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:06:22.170 --> 00:06:24.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ahh! Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:26.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My brain is fried.</b></Default>

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:27.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang in there, Yamada.</b></Default>

00:06:27.709 --> 00:06:29.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You still have 30 minutes
of class left.</b></Default>

00:06:29.709 --> 00:06:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's too long.</b></Default>

00:06:31.579 --> 00:06:33.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then take a quick five.</b></Default>

00:06:33.170 --> 00:06:35.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-All right!
-[sighs]</b></Default>

00:06:36.790 --> 00:06:39.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, do you guys know
about #DREAMING?</b></Default>

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, you believe in stuff
like that, Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:46.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only thing being taken on
seriously here</b></Default>

00:06:46.379 --> 00:06:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is your midterm scores.</b></Default>

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:50.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, one of my dreams came true.</b></Default>

00:06:50.790 --> 00:06:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just about a month ago</b></Default>

00:06:52.379 --> 00:06:54.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a dream where
I scored the winning point</b></Default>

00:06:54.459 --> 00:06:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a beach volleyball match
with a clean ace.</b></Default>

00:06:56.670 --> 00:06:58.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I posted it on DREAMING</b></Default>

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that's how things ended up
in the match on Sunday.</b></Default>

00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But isn't that just because
you practiced a whole bunch?</b></Default>

00:07:03.329 --> 00:07:05.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't believe in the occult.
Believe in yourself.</b></Default>

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know what to say
when you react like that.</b></Default>

00:07:08.329 --> 00:07:09.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just speaking the truth.</b></Default>

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even then</b></Default>

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'm not creepy, you little--
-Don't even start with me.</b></Default>

00:07:14.670 --> 00:07:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's try to keep it
down a bit, okay?</b></Default>

00:07:17.079 --> 00:07:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Otherwise, I'm gonna get
a scolding from Miss Futaba</b></Default>

00:07:19.579 --> 00:07:21.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's teaching her students
right next door.</b></Default>

00:07:21.579 --> 00:07:23.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[knocking on door]
-Here we go.</b></Default>

00:07:23.290 --> 00:07:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have a moment, sir?</b></Default>

00:07:25.079 --> 00:07:26.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! Uh, hey there, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:07:26.959 --> 00:07:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Nice to see you.</b></Default>

00:07:28.629 --> 00:07:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[reacts nervously]</b></Default>

00:07:29.879 --> 00:07:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I do something
for you, Himeji?</b></Default>

00:07:32.129 --> 00:07:33.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Mr. Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:36.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would it be all right with you
if I observed your class?</b></Default>

00:07:36.209 --> 00:07:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did tell you
Miss Futaba is better</b></Default>

00:07:38.079 --> 00:07:40.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you want a proper
understanding of math, didn't I?</b></Default>

00:07:40.670 --> 00:07:42.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, that's true</b></Default>

00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:44.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I just wanted to get
good test scores</b></Default>

00:07:44.459 --> 00:07:45.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'd recommend yourself.</b></Default>

00:07:45.829 --> 00:07:47.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is what I intended.</b></Default>

00:07:47.879 --> 00:07:49.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I've lost all confidence.</b></Default>

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, did something happen?</b></Default>

00:07:51.709 --> 00:07:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yamada got a 30% score.</b></Default>

00:07:53.750 --> 00:07:56.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, that's personal
information, Mr. Sakuta!</b></Default>

00:07:56.829 --> 00:07:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How stupid.</b></Default>

00:08:02.079 --> 00:08:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please hold the door</b></Default>

00:08:05.750 --> 00:08:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Looks like I'm safe.
-No, you're out.</b></Default>

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saying Mr. Azusagawa
every time is a lot.</b></Default>

00:08:10.459 --> 00:08:13.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>May I call you Mr. Sakuta?
You know, like Yamada does?</b></Default>

00:08:13.629 --> 00:08:16.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as you show me
more respect than Yamada does</b></Default>

00:08:16.209 --> 00:08:17.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't mind.</b></Default>

00:08:17.209 --> 00:08:19.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got it, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:08:24.129 --> 00:08:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji, do you take the train
from here?</b></Default>

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:28.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. My mom comes
to pick me up in her car.</b></Default>

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should be hearing
from her any minute.</b></Default>

00:08:30.920 --> 00:08:32.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you dropped it.</b></Default>

00:08:32.289 --> 00:08:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! That's okay.</b></Default>

00:08:33.379 --> 00:08:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[both grunt]</b></Default>

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oww!</b></Default>

00:08:36.169 --> 00:08:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry, Mr. Sakuta.
Are you okay?</b></Default>

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It might have split open in two.</b></Default>

00:08:41.330 --> 00:08:43.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no. Let me take a look.</b></Default>

00:08:44.129 --> 00:08:45.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.</b></Default>

00:08:45.169 --> 00:08:47.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your head
isn't even injured, sir.</b></Default>

00:08:48.419 --> 00:08:49.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here you go.</b></Default>

00:08:51.580 --> 00:08:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, thank you very much.</b></Default>

00:08:53.379 --> 00:08:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[elevator dings]</b></Default>

00:08:54.669 --> 00:08:56.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:58.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you'll excuse me here.</b></Default>

00:09:00.580 --> 00:09:02.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is her head made of cement
or something?</b></Default>

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:07.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, I'm back!</b></Default>

00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:09:12.460 --> 00:09:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello and welcome back home</b></Default>

00:09:14.669 --> 00:09:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you like some food?
Wanna take a bath?</b></Default>

00:09:17.669 --> 00:09:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or maybe more?</b></Default>

00:09:19.919 --> 00:09:21.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing, Zukki?</b></Default>

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard you guys
were having curry tonight.</b></Default>

00:09:24.039 --> 00:09:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'm here to partake
in its goodness.</b></Default>

00:09:26.129 --> 00:09:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki, this is a crucial
time for you</b></Default>

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:30.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you need to be
more careful of scandals.</b></Default>

00:09:30.210 --> 00:09:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the paparazzi managed
to get a picture</b></Default>

00:09:32.129 --> 00:09:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the caption would say</b></Default>

00:09:34.710 --> 00:09:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I hope our dinner helps
you land a curry commercial.</b></Default>

00:09:38.379 --> 00:09:40.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome home, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:09:40.210 --> 00:09:41.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome back, Big Brother.</b></Default>

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome back, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:47.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You pesky brats!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:49.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I won't let you get away{\i0}
{\i1}with this!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:09:49.710 --> 00:09:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Go, my minions!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:09:50.789 --> 00:09:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Capture them!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:09:53.669 --> 00:09:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow. It's a full house.</b></Default>

00:09:58.539 --> 00:10:01.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had everybody help me out
with chopping the vegetables.</b></Default>

00:10:04.419 --> 00:10:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Toyohama must have
done the potatoes.</b></Default>

00:10:06.879 --> 00:10:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quit your complaining and eat!</b></Default>

00:10:08.669 --> 00:10:11.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't even
started complaining.</b></Default>

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:14.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The eggplants must have been
chopped by Kaede.</b></Default>

00:10:14.539 --> 00:10:16.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please just eat your food
without complaining.</b></Default>

00:10:16.460 --> 00:10:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't even
started complaining.</b></Default>

00:10:19.289 --> 00:10:21.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The zucchini
must have been Hirokawa.</b></Default>

00:10:21.710 --> 00:10:22.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is Zukki.</b></Default>

00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:23.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct!</b></Default>

00:10:27.169 --> 00:10:29.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm? Oh, wow, Mai</b></Default>

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad you like it.</b></Default>

00:10:31.629 --> 00:10:34.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My perfect Mai
is beautiful as always today.</b></Default>

00:10:34.750 --> 00:10:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah!</b></Default>

00:10:36.129 --> 00:10:38.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something I wanted
to give you, Big Brother.</b></Default>

00:10:38.210 --> 00:10:40.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Concert tickets
for the campus festival.</b></Default>

00:10:40.129 --> 00:10:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please come watch with Mai.</b></Default>

00:10:41.830 --> 00:10:44.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, okay</b></Default>

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:46.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, Mai, don't you work
on Sunday?</b></Default>

00:10:46.789 --> 00:10:48.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I plan to tour
the campus festival with you</b></Default>

00:10:48.879 --> 00:10:50.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I left my schedule open.</b></Default>

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, this is news to me.</b></Default>

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:54.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because if I did end up
having to work</b></Default>

00:10:54.500 --> 00:10:55.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and had to cancel last minute</b></Default>

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would have to play along with
one of your whims in return.</b></Default>

00:10:58.629 --> 00:11:01.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:11:03.169 --> 00:11:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, can you swap shifts
at the restaurant with me?</b></Default>

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm also going to the concert
with Komi, so no.</b></Default>

00:11:09.629 --> 00:11:11.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll ask Koga later.</b></Default>

00:11:11.750 --> 00:11:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[KAEDE[ Want me to ask her now?
-Yes, please.</b></Default>

00:11:14.580 --> 00:11:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on a sec.</b></Default>

00:11:16.129 --> 00:11:18.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[notification dings]
-Uh, she replied.</b></Default>

00:11:18.500 --> 00:11:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She answers texts quickly.</b></Default>

00:11:20.169 --> 00:11:22.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She says, "I want to eat
cream puffs from the station."</b></Default>

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:25.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell her I'll buy her ten
next time.</b></Default>

00:11:25.210 --> 00:11:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She also said</b></Default>

00:11:27.289 --> 00:11:29.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing less from Laplace's
petite devil.</b></Default>

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:33.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm looking forward to the
campus festival date with Mai.</b></Default>

00:11:33.169 --> 00:11:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should be looking forward
to the concert, dummy.</b></Default>

00:11:36.129 --> 00:11:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, Big Sis, I'm gonna
head back with Uzuki now</b></Default>

00:11:39.129 --> 00:11:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and fill up the tub.</b></Default>

00:11:40.460 --> 00:11:41.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh? Please do.</b></Default>

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for having me.</b></Default>

00:11:43.580 --> 00:11:45.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki, you sleeping
over at Mai's?</b></Default>

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:48.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs mischievously]</b></Default>

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:50.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then</b></Default>

00:11:50.629 --> 00:11:51.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede giggles]</b></Default>

00:11:53.460 --> 00:11:55.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna go take a bath too.</b></Default>

00:11:55.460 --> 00:11:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kaede</b></Default>

00:11:57.629 --> 00:11:59.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't use it
for anything strange, okay?</b></Default>

00:11:59.789 --> 00:12:01.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only needed
to look something up.</b></Default>

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right. Big Brother</b></Default>

00:12:05.039 --> 00:12:06.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this was left for you.</b></Default>

00:12:07.629 --> 00:12:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:09.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:12.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SHOKO MAKINOHARA</b></Default>

00:12:16.210 --> 00:12:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Is it Autumn already{\i0}
{\i1}over there?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:18.330 --> 00:12:20.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}We're still in the middle{\i0}
{\i1}of summer over here.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:20.750 --> 00:12:24.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Here's photo proof.{\i0}
{\i1}It's me, Shoko! {\i0}[giggles]</b></Default>

00:12:24.669 --> 00:12:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I LOVE YOU!</b></Default>

00:12:26.419 --> 00:12:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that Shoko-chan?</b></Default>

00:12:27.830 --> 00:12:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She looks more and more
like Shoko-san lately.</b></Default>

00:12:30.169 --> 00:12:31.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She certainly does.</b></Default>

00:12:31.669 --> 00:12:33.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna have to keep
my eye out.</b></Default>

00:12:33.710 --> 00:12:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:12:34.919 --> 00:12:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In due time</b></Default>

00:12:36.879 --> 00:12:38.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who was your first crush.</b></Default>

00:12:38.250 --> 00:12:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:12:40.080 --> 00:12:41.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you happy?</b></Default>

00:12:41.669 --> 00:12:43.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I am happy.</b></Default>

00:12:43.289 --> 00:12:45.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause when spring comes</b></Default>

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:48.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be the high school student
she wished to be.</b></Default>

00:12:48.250 --> 00:12:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes me sound
like the villain of this story.</b></Default>

00:12:53.039 --> 00:12:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:12:56.629 --> 00:12:59.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was the thing you wanted
to look up the DREAMING tag?</b></Default>

00:12:59.289 --> 00:13:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I'd read
a bit more about it.</b></Default>

00:13:01.330 --> 00:13:02.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I WAS BUYING TOILET PAPER</b></Default>

00:13:02.460 --> 00:13:03.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I TOOK MY SHOES OFF
AT THE CASH REGISTER.</b></Default>

00:13:05.379 --> 00:13:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:13:06.539 --> 00:13:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you think about
your classmates from back then?</b></Default>

00:13:09.330 --> 00:13:12.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-My classmates?
-From your middle school days.</b></Default>

00:13:12.460 --> 00:13:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We haven't talked much about</b></Default>

00:13:13.830 --> 00:13:15.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what those times
were like for you.</b></Default>

00:13:15.750 --> 00:13:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I don't really think
about them at all.</b></Default>

00:13:18.789 --> 00:13:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With Kaede being bullied</b></Default>

00:13:20.169 --> 00:13:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's the only thing
I could think about.</b></Default>

00:13:22.539 --> 00:13:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>AZUSAGAWA'S READING
BUT IGNORING AGAIN?DIE, KAEDE</b></Default>

00:13:23.879 --> 00:13:25.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Nobody would even{\i0}
{\i1}try to believe me{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:25.250 --> 00:13:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}about puberty syndrome{\i0}
{\i1}being real.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:27.539 --> 00:13:29.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Kaede was always{\i0}
{\i1}cooped up in her room{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:29.539 --> 00:13:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and lost her memory.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:31.419 --> 00:13:33.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}My mom lost her mind as well{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:33.289 --> 00:13:35.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and that fragmented our family.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:35.789 --> 00:13:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

00:13:39.879 --> 00:13:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:13:43.789 --> 00:13:44.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:13:48.330 --> 00:13:51.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then you met your
first crush for the first time.</b></Default>

00:13:51.210 --> 00:13:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And a while after that</b></Default>

00:13:54.039 --> 00:13:56.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should really forget
about that already.</b></Default>

00:13:56.460 --> 00:13:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

00:13:59.879 --> 00:14:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but things started to get better
in high school.</b></Default>

00:14:02.289 --> 00:14:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I became close friends{\i0}
{\i1}with Kunimi and Futaba</b></Default>

00:14:05.750 --> 00:14:07.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and I had you, Mai.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:07.460 --> 00:14:09.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I got to know{\i0}
{\i1}Toyohama and Koga</b></Default>

00:14:09.710 --> 00:14:11.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and so many things happened.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Kaede started{\i0}
{\i1}feeling better too.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:18.669 --> 00:14:22.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it's more like I didn't
let my classmates bother me.</b></Default>

00:14:23.789 --> 00:14:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, in that case, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:14:27.830 --> 00:14:29.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Forgiven her?</b></Default>

00:14:29.879 --> 00:14:31.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa's lost it.</b></Default>

00:14:31.669 --> 00:14:33.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think he's gone insane.</b></Default>

00:14:35.379 --> 00:14:38.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all whispering]</b></Default>

00:14:44.460 --> 00:14:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:14:46.169 --> 00:14:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, it's nothing.</b></Default>

00:14:47.879 --> 00:14:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like Akagi
did anything to me directly.</b></Default>

00:14:51.330 --> 00:14:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But for some reason</b></Default>

00:14:53.919 --> 00:14:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:14:55.039 --> 00:14:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, it's not what
you're thinking.</b></Default>

00:14:58.379 --> 00:15:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever your connection
to her may be</b></Default>

00:15:00.750 --> 00:15:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure
if your reunion with her</b></Default>

00:15:02.629 --> 00:15:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has anything to do with
her usage of the dreaming tag.</b></Default>

00:15:05.289 --> 00:15:07.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you and I know
all too well</b></Default>

00:15:07.419 --> 00:15:09.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just how cruel and disastrous
changing the future can be.</b></Default>

00:15:09.539 --> 00:15:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DREAMT OF A TEST I FINISHED</b></Default>

00:15:11.169 --> 00:15:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she's doing it
for someone who's dear to her</b></Default>

00:15:13.789 --> 00:15:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't really say
she should stop.</b></Default>

00:15:16.629 --> 00:15:18.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would do the same.</b></Default>

00:15:18.419 --> 00:15:20.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mai, you're also opposed</b></Default>

00:15:20.210 --> 00:15:22.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to her becoming
a hero of justice, right?</b></Default>

00:15:22.629 --> 00:15:25.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Yes. And that's because
we both know that</b></Default>

00:15:25.250 --> 00:15:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one person's happiness may be
someone else's misfortune.</b></Default>

00:15:28.419 --> 00:15:29.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's true.</b></Default>

00:15:29.750 --> 00:15:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But with how we're talking</b></Default>

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:34.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that are getting in the way
of the hero of justice.</b></Default>

00:15:34.539 --> 00:15:36.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then</b></Default>

00:15:36.710 --> 00:15:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we should play the part, right</b></Default>

00:15:41.539 --> 00:15:42.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>CHOOSE A PROFILE PICTURE</b></Default>

00:15:42.710 --> 00:15:44.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Natsuno</b></Default>

00:15:45.539 --> 00:15:46.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[meows]</b></Default>

00:15:49.789 --> 00:15:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A BOY TRIPPED AND IS CRYING
IN FRONT OF THE CLOCK TOWER.</b></Default>

00:15:52.789 --> 00:15:55.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 6TH
SILVER LEAF FESTIVAL</b></Default>

00:15:55.169 --> 00:15:58.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ band sings in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:16:00.789 --> 00:16:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:16:07.539 --> 00:16:11.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ band sings in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:16:18.460 --> 00:16:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:16:23.080 --> 00:16:25.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HOST] Thank you for that
lovely performance.</b></Default>

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But before you leave the stage</b></Default>

00:16:27.330 --> 00:16:28.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how about an encore?</b></Default>

00:16:28.710 --> 00:16:30.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you all want to hear
