00:16:30.460 --> 00:16:31.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, everyone</b></Default>

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:33.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>let's keep the hype up
to the very end!</b></Default>

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:36.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:16:45.210 --> 00:16:46.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

00:16:46.419 --> 00:16:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Great job out there.</b></Default>

00:16:47.789 --> 00:16:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was longer than expected.</b></Default>

00:16:49.289 --> 00:16:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, we weren't planning
for that surprise encore.</b></Default>

00:16:52.129 --> 00:16:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The host got totally
carried away, didn't he?</b></Default>

00:16:54.710 --> 00:16:56.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But everyone seemed happy</b></Default>

00:16:56.129 --> 00:16:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm glad
we went through with it.</b></Default>

00:16:57.919 --> 00:16:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you guys going to present</b></Default>

00:16:59.330 --> 00:17:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the Mr. and Miss Campus
contest after this?</b></Default>

00:17:01.879 --> 00:17:04.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh. So before that's over</b></Default>

00:17:04.920 --> 00:17:07.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must get
the chocolate-covered bananas.</b></Default>

00:17:15.710 --> 00:17:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yakisoba</b></Default>

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>boba, takoyaki</b></Default>

00:17:18.670 --> 00:17:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>chocolate-covered banana</b></Default>

00:17:21.329 --> 00:17:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The scale of this festival
is so much bigger</b></Default>

00:17:23.460 --> 00:17:24.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than ones from our high school.</b></Default>

00:17:24.960 --> 00:17:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could really go
for a taco myself.</b></Default>

00:17:27.329 --> 00:17:29.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Then do you wanna buy one
for us as well?</b></Default>

00:17:32.329 --> 00:17:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[chuckles] Oh, welcome.</b></Default>

00:17:33.630 --> 00:17:34.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}TACO/POTSTICKERS 200 YEN
TEA 150 YEN</b></Default>

00:17:34.670 --> 00:17:36.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I have two tacos, please?</b></Default>

00:17:36.630 --> 00:17:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And one with extra salsa</b></Default>

00:17:39.130 --> 00:17:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, it's Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:17:40.750 --> 00:17:41.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. You're right.</b></Default>

00:17:42.250 --> 00:17:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They were at the mixer.</b></Default>

00:17:44.039 --> 00:17:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As you're already aware</b></Default>

00:17:47.329 --> 00:17:49.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Here in the flesh.</b></Default>

00:17:49.420 --> 00:17:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Is this real?
-She actually just bowed at me!</b></Default>

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:53.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nuh-uh. She was bowing at me.</b></Default>

00:17:53.329 --> 00:17:55.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Thanks for waiting.</b></Default>

00:17:55.170 --> 00:17:57.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two aren't cosplaying?</b></Default>

00:17:57.130 --> 00:17:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want to see me
in a nurse outfit?</b></Default>

00:17:59.579 --> 00:18:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to</b></Default>

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:06.579 --> 00:18:09.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here's the spare mayo
and salsa you asked for.</b></Default>

00:18:09.289 --> 00:18:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for that, Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:13.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like we're about
to run out of cabbage.</b></Default>

00:18:13.130 --> 00:18:15.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The yakisoba stall said
they'd share some of theirs.</b></Default>

00:18:15.960 --> 00:18:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NURSING DEPARTMENT</b></Default>

00:18:16.960 --> 00:18:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anything else
that you need restocked?</b></Default>

00:18:18.170 --> 00:18:19.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, we'll be fine for now.</b></Default>

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should stay over
at the flea market, Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:18:22.329 --> 00:18:25.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With Fukuyama and company here</b></Default>

00:18:25.670 --> 00:18:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, thank you for coming by
on such short notice, you guys.</b></Default>

00:18:28.829 --> 00:18:31.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry you had
to take my place.</b></Default>

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what happened
to Akagi's arm?</b></Default>

00:18:39.460 --> 00:18:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She tried to support someone
who was staggering on the stairs</b></Default>

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the train station.</b></Default>

00:18:46.380 --> 00:18:49.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, you can go ahead
and check up on Akagi.</b></Default>

00:18:49.250 --> 00:18:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll deliver all the treats
we got backstage.</b></Default>

00:18:51.500 --> 00:18:53.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, well</b></Default>

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but, uh, what should we do
about our taco?</b></Default>

00:18:57.460 --> 00:18:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's have it now. Ah!</b></Default>

00:19:01.630 --> 00:19:02.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:05.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm. Tasty!</b></Default>

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll head over for a bit.</b></Default>

00:19:20.250 --> 00:19:21.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:19:32.329 --> 00:19:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never knew how boring
being injured was.</b></Default>

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems no one needs my help
when I'm like this.</b></Default>

00:19:37.579 --> 00:19:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody wants other people
to think they're evil monsters</b></Default>

00:19:40.170 --> 00:19:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who force someone to work
when they're injured.</b></Default>

00:19:42.500 --> 00:19:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, they're more worried
about their image than me.</b></Default>

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doesn't that make
you feel more at ease?</b></Default>

00:19:51.750 --> 00:19:54.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I showed them my pictures
from Halloween</b></Default>

00:19:54.329 --> 00:19:55.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Chiharu started saying</b></Default>

00:19:55.920 --> 00:19:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that we should dress up
like this for the taco shop.</b></Default>

00:19:59.079 --> 00:20:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saki and I were
against the idea, but...</b></Default>

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:02.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's nice and all</b></Default>

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:04.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm less curious
about that trendy outfit</b></Default>

00:20:05.039 --> 00:20:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and more about what happened
to your arm.</b></Default>

00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From what I hear</b></Default>

00:20:09.710 --> 00:20:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you stopped someone
from falling down stairs.</b></Default>

00:20:14.579 --> 00:20:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess I went against
the kind advice you gave me.</b></Default>

00:20:18.329 --> 00:20:20.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must think
I'm a dumb woman, huh?</b></Default>

00:20:20.670 --> 00:20:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's your dominant arm, right?
You okay?</b></Default>

00:20:23.829 --> 00:20:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks worse than it is</b></Default>

00:20:25.329 --> 00:20:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's just a sprain</b></Default>

00:20:28.039 --> 00:20:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give it about a week
and it will heal.</b></Default>

00:20:32.130 --> 00:20:33.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:20:33.880 --> 00:20:35.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you happen to remember
what you wrote</b></Default>

00:20:35.670 --> 00:20:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for your graduation essay
in middle school?</b></Default>

00:20:38.539 --> 00:20:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not at all.</b></Default>

00:20:39.670 --> 00:20:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I threw away my yearbook
and those memories when I moved.</b></Default>

00:20:43.039 --> 00:20:44.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I remember.</b></Default>

00:20:45.579 --> 00:20:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I wrote in it...</b></Default>

00:20:47.289 --> 00:20:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and what you wrote.</b></Default>

00:20:48.539 --> 00:20:51.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd definitely like you
to forget what I wrote.</b></Default>

00:20:51.170 --> 00:20:53.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure it couldn't have been
anything good.</b></Default>

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not true.</b></Default>

00:20:54.579 --> 00:20:55.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

00:20:55.920 --> 00:20:57.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, you wrote</b></Default>

00:20:58.000 --> 00:21:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Someday, I think
I'd like to reach kindness."</b></Default>

00:21:01.079 --> 00:21:02.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:21:03.170 --> 00:21:06.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, have you reached
your goal, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:21:08.420 --> 00:21:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, what about you, Akagi?</b></Default>

00:21:10.829 --> 00:21:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think you can become
your ideal person</b></Default>

00:21:13.039 --> 00:21:14.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you envisioned
in middle school?</b></Default>

00:21:15.920 --> 00:21:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is a hero of justice something</b></Default>

00:21:17.829 --> 00:21:20.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that even adults dream
about becoming?</b></Default>

00:21:20.079 --> 00:21:23.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then would it have been better
for that girl to get hurt?</b></Default>

00:21:23.170 --> 00:21:25.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I just feel that
it would have been better</b></Default>

00:21:25.130 --> 00:21:26.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you didn't end up injured.</b></Default>

00:21:26.750 --> 00:21:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be careful from now on.</b></Default>

00:21:28.710 --> 00:21:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No intention of quitting, huh?</b></Default>

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:32.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look. Over there.</b></Default>

00:21:32.380 --> 00:21:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>POTTERY</b></Default>

00:21:33.380 --> 00:21:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm running that stall</b></Default>

00:21:34.380 --> 00:21:36.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with middle school kids
that I volunteered to tutor.</b></Default>

00:21:37.079 --> 00:21:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're all kids who became
unable to attend school.</b></Default>

00:21:40.710 --> 00:21:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're selling some pottery
we all made together.</b></Default>

00:21:43.289 --> 00:21:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please take a look.</b></Default>

00:21:44.789 --> 00:21:46.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got somewhere
to go right now.</b></Default>

00:21:50.960 --> 00:21:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's the clock tower</b></Default>

00:21:54.329 --> 00:21:55.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing's going to happen.</b></Default>

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:57.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:21:57.170 --> 00:21:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saw the DREAMING
tag post, right?</b></Default>

00:22:00.380 --> 00:22:02.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one about a boy who trips
and starts crying?</b></Default>

00:22:03.460 --> 00:22:05.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I made the whole{\i0}
{\i1}thing up myself{\i0}.</b></Default>

00:22:05.170 --> 00:22:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A BOY TRIPPED AND IS CRYING
IN FRONT OF THE CLOCK TOWER.</b></Default>

00:22:08.460 --> 00:22:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's good.</b></Default>

00:22:09.630 --> 00:22:12.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad there isn't
a crying boy over there.</b></Default>

00:22:13.329 --> 00:22:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As for you, don't do that.</b></Default>

00:22:15.829 --> 00:22:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're university students now.</b></Default>

00:22:18.710 --> 00:22:21.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, you're right.
We're university students now.</b></Default>

00:22:21.670 --> 00:22:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, don't copy me.</b></Default>

00:22:23.329 --> 00:22:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

00:22:30.710 --> 00:22:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cries]</b></Default>

00:22:34.170 --> 00:22:35.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:44.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry. I'm okay.</b></Default>

00:22:44.710 --> 00:22:46.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi, are you...</b></Default>

00:22:47.539 --> 00:22:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nothing.</b></Default>

00:22:49.210 --> 00:22:51.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It just happens sometimes.</b></Default>

00:22:51.670 --> 00:22:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:22:55.460 --> 00:22:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.579 --> 00:23:03.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF A NIGHTINGALE</b></Default>

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] {\i1}Oh, Sakuta.{\i0}
{\i1}You're such a rascal.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE - #6 YOU AND I
WITHIN THE REALM OF MEMORIES</b></Default>
